é Antoine Ferchault de</persName><note type="lebensdaten">(1683-1757)</note></person><person><persName key="pers_DE-588-117619515">Saurin, Joseph</persName><note type="lebensdaten">(1655-1737)</note></person><person><persName key="pers_DE-588-12209025X">Werenfels, Samuel</persName><note type="lebensdaten">(1657-1740)</note></person></listPerson></abstract><textClass/></profileDesc><revisionDesc status="transkribiert">
